    <mainBody>
      <paragraph eId="para_1" class="MercuryDocument">
        <content eId="para_1__content">
          <p xml:space="preserve"> At its 63rd plenary meeting, on 21 March 2024, on the proposal of the Secretary-General,<authorialNote marker="1" placement="bottom" eId="authorialNote_1"><p xml:space="preserve"> <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/78/785">A/78/785</a>.</p></authorialNote> the General Assembly approved, notwithstanding section XI, paragraph 22, of resolution <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/59/276">59/276</a> of 23 December 2004, the exceptional extension of the term of Gilles Michaud (Canada) as Under-Secretary-General for Safety and Security by two years, until 30 June 2026.</p>
        </content>
      </paragraph>
